achine. #275 (2023-10-31T10:25:28.517Z)","1201.0.21":"* Add Faster Work Module\n* Minor improvement in command\n* Limit the number of chaining of Dummy Block. #278 (2023-10-28T10:17:03.677Z)","1201.0.17":"* Add Faster Work Module\n* Minor improvement in command (2023-09-02T05:28:13.285Z)","1201.0.15":"* Change layout of buttons in Flexible Marker GUI\n* Change internal behavior of Flexible Marker GUI to prevent crash [#271](https://github.com/Kotori316/QuarryPlus/issues/271) (2023-08-26T08:53:23.287Z)","1201.0.14-SNAPSHOT":"* Update for 1.20/1.20.1\n* Add progress of QuarryPlus and ChunkDestroyer in Status Checker\n* Change format of poses in Status Checker\n* Fix crash related to FTB Chunks\n* Check chunk existence in Chunk Destroyer\n* Fix a bug of save/load of Chunk Destroyer\n* Add server config to disable machine in specific dimension\n* The range of Flexible Marker is now configurable\n* Fix deadlock with some item transfer mod (2023-08-25T14:25:24.008Z)","1201.0.1-SNAPSHOT":"2023-08-03T03:33:22.717Z","1201.0.0-SNAPSHOT":"2023-08-01T03:00:00.142Z"}}
